"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Some murmurs about GameFi:\\n\\n1) GameFi is actually \\\"Fi\\\" instead of \\\"Game\\\", the game is terrible and not fun at all\\n\\n2) But it doesn't mean GameFi is not a hot/right topic. Money game always brings people in, which grows the ecosystem\\n\\n3) Would GameFi bubble? I don't think so. Some of so-called \\\"Industry funds\\\" such as Animoca Brands, who is keeping investing GameFi projects, will maintain the \\\"bubble\\\". Even people thinks the evaluation is too large for a game company, but the bubble can't be eliminated\\n\\n4) So, if you want to find a fun game to play. Go back to your Steam or any laptop games. (Or if you like mobile games) GameFi is definitely less fun, at least 1-3 years.\",\"timestamp\":1636622111,\"title\":\"Some thoughts for GameFi\"},\"digest\":\"W9H7DRNQM3TZdWzmjup6Q4toHbNdaqMnybZyZ_ZovDQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xb1a413Cf4A041aE76087c092702a52Ab0E2bDa3C\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"PCkCj80lcKSqXjZzncDCizUorVViAmqvIg9BsmtLjUo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"F2wn5zO6Dkp7NE_IbBQwhJsaoE6Lt1new4uc_ApavXg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Z8gzNNndMASBha3h8fp0jCJ9oAbFLxRVJTMyK79w18aGWewQh9t-3HRb2qnxddz8B5-SWLwzHnoWdHbwzMwOPg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x86218149710eac97ed3d8051973abf0f6d488e9327595de5e6831c4ec8cb6d3e789ea36f6cd8736007a68d20bbaa8d490f9c3956be3b52fbce470f9aa81d67e61c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"PCkCj80lcKSqXjZzncDCizUorVViAmqvIg9BsmtLjUo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"F2wn5zO6Dkp7NE_IbBQwhJsaoE6Lt1new4uc_ApavXg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"W9H7DRNQM3TZdWzmjup6Q4toHbNdaqMnybZyZ_ZovDQ\"}"